{
  "stem": "11611.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to the desk of the Grand Hotel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I announced my name and said I was here for duty, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The man at the desk said, I don't know anything about you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You don't mean anything to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why don't you try the hotel about two blocks away called the Deutscher Hof.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I had all my luggage with me, which was one suitcase.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had to walk two blocks over to the Deutscher Hof.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I got there, there was a tall, good looking German who was there in-- had arrived-- and he spoke English-- who had arrived in Nuremberg as a witness.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't think to ask a witness for who or what.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was pretty damn naive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he wanted to know where he was supposed to be put up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think he was basically a Berliner.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at the Deutscher Hof, they had a record on me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They knew I was supposed to be there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they called me an army taxi.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And meanwhile, I was standing around the desk and this German was trying to find out where he was supposed to stay.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said, you're on your own.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We don't care where you stay.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Go find yourself someplace.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By this time, It must have been about 1 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The fellow looked OK to me, so I-- as soon as they announced that I had a place, I said, come on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Join me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You can stay at my place, wherever it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I took the German with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then, in the morning we took a bus to the court house where I formally checked in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the bus was filled with Nuremberg prosecution staff people, mostly administrative people, interpreters.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
